Package com.challenge.pom

Class SearchPage

java.lang.Object
com.challenge.pom.Base
com.challenge.pom.SearchPage
public class SearchPage extends Base
This class extends the Base wrapper class and serves the same purpose, having this class it won't be necessary to modify the test in case something happens with current way to perform action. Also, this class main purpose is to wrap all possible actions that can be performed in the search page
Author:
Jorge Canario
